    rdfs:comment "User performed two repo-settings changes: (a) switched the default branch to main; (b) set Pages source to GitHub Actions. Repository docs reconciled: CLAUDE.md branch-policy paragraph rewritten (main is default; development on feature branches off main; PRs target main; direct pushes to main require explicit instruction); CLAUDE.md gains a 'Pages source' subsection naming pages.yml as the canonical deploy mechanism. agents/orchestrator.md refusal-conditions updated. doc/methodology.md gains a 'Branch and deployment policy' subsection. pages.yml itself does not change; its configure-pages + upload-pages-artefact + deploy-pages chain is the canonical pattern for 'Source = GitHub Actions'."@en ;
