    fair2r:promotedToPaper "yes" ;
    rdfs:comment "Graduated to paper text 2026-05-06 as the second-order finding in paper/sections/authors-note.tex, *What surprised me about the cooperation*. The coupling-rule formulation (accelerator on the prose-craft side; cultural blender if it crosses into the abstracting layer) supplies the reason the human-deciding / model-drafting partition matters."@en ;
    dcterms:created "2026-05-06"^^xsd:date .

